ot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42417ec elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"42417ec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Prioridade do Google no Mobile-First Indexing\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bfe641a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bfe641a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e3333ab elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e3333ab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Em mar\u00e7o de 2021, o Google implementou o &#8220;Mobile-First Indexing&#8221; como padr\u00e3o. Isso significa que o Google agora utiliza a vers\u00e3o m\u00f3vel do conte\u00fado de um site para classific\u00e1-lo nos resultados de pesquisa. Portanto, se o seu site n\u00e3o estiver otimizado para dispositivos m\u00f3veis, ele poder\u00e1 ser penalizado nas classifica\u00e7\u00f5es do Google.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c2b7c3a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c2b7c3a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e6cbfad elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e6cbfad\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>1. Design responsivo<\/strong><\/p><p>Um design responsivo \u00e9 a base da otimiza\u00e7\u00e3o para dispositivos m\u00f3veis. Ele permite que o conte\u00fado do seu site se adapte automaticamente ao tamanho da tela do dispositivo em que est\u00e1 sendo exibido. Com um design responsivo, seu site parecer\u00e1 e funcionar\u00e1 de forma eficaz em smartphones, tablets e desktops.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-104c0a8 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"104c0a8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05b8048 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"05b8048\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2. Velocidade de carregamento<\/strong><\/p><p>A velocidade de carregamento \u00e9 crucial para dispositivos m\u00f3veis, onde as conex\u00f5es podem ser mais lentas. Certifique-se de que seu site carregue rapidamente em dispositivos m\u00f3veis. Isso envolve otimizar imagens, minimizar o uso de scripts pesados e utilizar o armazenamento em cache.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d26ff0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1d26ff0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class